setAnnotation() - 类 中的方法uflp.AnnotationBenders
添加 Benders 注释
1 创建 IloCplex.LongAnnotation 注释对象

Step 0: Initialization
Step 1: Selection of the vertex to be treated
Step 2: Exploration of the successor of the current vertex

Step 4: Filtering.
